data.description: Lovely, 4bed/3bath home, located in the Master Planned Providence Community, featuring laminate flooring in the main living areas, ceiling fans & window coverings throughout! Bed & Bath downstairs; 3 addt'l bedrooms upstairs,along w/a loft that can be used as an office,addt'l living space or playroom. The kitchen boasts granite counters,stainless steel appliances & tile flooring. Northern Terrace offers a clubhouse, community pool, spa, bbq & play area. There are 2 parks in Providence. Huckleberry Park is across the street from Northern Terrace, where you will enjoy 2 tennis courts, pickleball courts, playgrounds, multi-sport grass field, full-court basketball, picnic areas, walking trails, & a dog park. At Knickerbocker Park, you can enjoy the Baseball Diamond, spacious multi-use grass field, splashpad, fitness stations, Playground, walking trails, picnic tables, & dog park. Easy access to the 215 freeway, restaurants & shopping. Come & see this spectacular home before it's gone!
